{"tid":897702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民建聯與街坊搭乘直通巴「港珠澳大橋首發遊」，市民親身感受這項「超級工程」的魅力，讚不絕口","createTime":"2018-11-11T06:59:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-11T10:39:22.000Z","uid":129134,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"818f8969fc2986ec8fcda1019259c3404eb1542c","tid":897702,"uid":129134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T06:59:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uctvgBf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuctvgBf.jpg&h=6c4b60ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kexgb9A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkexgb9A.jpg&h=6c997d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋24日正式通車。民建聯與街坊搭乘直通巴「港珠澳大橋首發遊」，市民親身感受這項「超級工程」的魅力，讚不絕口。<br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋配合「三地三檢」通關模式，乘客需在香港口岸人工島下車進入旅檢大樓，完成離境安檢。旅檢大樓寬敞明亮，清晰且具有人性化的指示標誌，令市民遊客可以快速通關。過關上橋，大橋雄偉壯觀，全長55公里，橋身呈流線型，車輛在橋上行駛平穩通暢。<br />\n<br />\n此趟港珠澳大橋體驗之旅，省時高效、方便快捷。大橋拉近了粵港澳三地之間的距離，相信粵港澳大灣區「一小時生活圈」的理想布局，亦會很快實現。"},{"pid":"17b5703b0de0d4c7385eba41f425e7d71b064f12","tid":897702,"uid":221265,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T07:40:18.000Z","msg":"全車垃圾廢老"},{"pid":"d410a315d998398680c4e1d2da1f2c737bba236f","tid":897702,"uid":30169,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T07:41:32.000Z","msg":"番唔番到黎？"},{"pid":"b2d74c113d85ac865bf4e4a83cca4ca59812259a","tid":897702,"uid":129134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T10:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75953560efda1b7c9aff7f0cd29d0daaa7a074b","tid":897702,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T10:39:22.000Z","msg":"民賤聯支持者真係有樣睇，物以類聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}